high_descs: go forward to the left face the toilet
pick up the spray bottle that is on top of the water tank
turn to the left go to the right facing the sink
put the spray on top of the sink
turn to the right , go left turn to the right again face the toilet
pick up the other spray bottle that is on top of the water tank
turn to the left go right facing the sink
put the spray bottle on top of the sink
anns.task_desc: put 2 spray bottles on top of the sink

high_descs: Move forward toward the shower, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost spray bottle from the back of the toilet.
Turn left and move forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the spray bottle on the counter, to the left of the sink.
Turn around, walk toward the door, then turn left to go toward the shower, then turn left to face the toilet.
Pick up the spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Turn left and move forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the spray bottle on the counter, to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles on the counter.

high_descs: Face the front of the toilet
Grab the spray bottle off of the top of the toilet on the left
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the bottle down to the left of the sink
Turn right and face the front of the toilet
Grab the spray bottle off of the top of the toilet
Turn left and go to the sink
Put the bottle down to the left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Putting two spray bottles on the counter near the sink
